.PD 0
.TP
.B MPI_SUCCESS 
- No error; MPI routine completed successfully.
.PD 1
.PD 0
.TP
.B MPI_T_ERR_NOT_INITIALIZED 
- The MPI tool information interface is not initialized.
.PD 1
.PD 0
.TP
.B MPI_T_ERR_INVALID_INDEX 
- Index is invalid or has been deleted.
.PD 1
